显示别名，能显示数字的全部转化成数字。\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@fbc</span>-yellow-<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\">&gt;</span>-l  仅列出有在 Listen (监听) 的服務状态\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@fbc</span>-yellow-<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\">&gt;</span>-p  显示建立相关链接的程序名\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@fbc</span>-yellow-<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\">&gt;</span>-r  显示路由信息，路由表\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@fbc</span>-yellow-<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\">&gt;</span>-e  显示扩展信息，例如uid等\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@fbc</span>-yellow-<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\">&gt;</span>-s  按各个协议进行统计\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@fbc</span>-yellow-<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\">&gt;</span>-c  每隔一个固定时间，执行该netstat命令。\n\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@h4</span>-安装vim\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@code</span>--@[&gt; apt-get install vim-gtk]@ \\\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@h4</span>-RPM安装mysql（centos7）\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@h5</span>-安装\n<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: #00c0ff;\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"\">@code</span>--@[&gt; rpm -ivh MySQL-server-5.6.15-1.el6.x86_64.rpm\n&gt; rpm -ivh MySQL-devel-5.6.15-1.el6.x8